WSV&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.frmq2-1.fna&amp;oh=c094ee30f2c03b1d0fdf38129357b815&amp;oe=5FCAF517\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.frmq2-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F14064036_1178205372242628_4371696019847548547_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D9267fe%26_nc_ohc%3DLl_xcz5Wz0oAX-ewWSV%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.frmq2-1.fna%26oh%3Dc094ee30f2c03b1d0fdf38129357b815%26oe%3D5FCAF517&h=3039ef2f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:04:26.000Z","msg":"熱民行得好前"},{"pid":"4a7d62ac07b76bd270922f5984331dbab30aed42","tid":2272572,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83bba86af706826d431cd58a5ba54a9f3f4c3199","tid":2272572,"uid":120229,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:54:10.000Z","msg":"我既意思係，例如，有個家長想幫個小朋友報一對一游水堂，咁佢住黃大仙區，星期六下午先有時間<br />\n<br />\n咁就幫佢根據翻上邊既條件黎配對翻個教練"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:06:50.000Z","msg":"有無得好似黃的台咁做法填完資料等師父接單"},{"pid":"6b28234f94c4ba00be6d8162728284cc9524782a","tid":2272572,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:07:07.000Z","msg":"難d, 你都識講黃既教練係佔多，咁做反而仲少左班藍學生 ，本身既黃學生 又可能轉左去其他黃教練"},{"pid":"6547696780d0a8b9b8cb970679f04531a4da7ce0","tid":2272572,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T07:09:38.000Z","msg":"其實有而且亦都好易就做到<br />\n<br />\n1) 體育YOUTUBER育成 接黃店宣傳JOB養活自己<br />\n2) 代表香港 (或好似賭聖咁代表中華民國)出戰國際賽<br />\n3) 建立香港人認受身份<br />\n<br />\n但咁同體育或運動員身份無任何關係 可能對於比較傳統MINDSET嘅人較難接受<br />\n<br />\n但RMBJ都係用運動員身份發揮政治力量 (甚至公然比錢破產人士/在獄人士買票) 而運動係國與國博奕中一向充當重要政治作用"},{"pid":"4555cbaa141d587c940a93d9543865e693d64d3b","tid":2272572,"uid":94613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1133b423705467e8efae19f2c8763551a1ba560b","tid":2272572,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"539521c2c6f04d74767cf348064a7b3f652d1435","tid":2272572,"uid":73381,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T06:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://